summary: This is a texture overhaul for female bodies
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/DSJminv.png[/img][/center] [font=Georgia][size=5][i]Dragon Girl[/i][/size][/font] is a female body texture replace that adds very Nordic tattoos that any Dragoborn Girl should have. Feel Nordic as fueghck when you are driving the Imperial dogs from your lands!!! A must have for any true daughter of Skyrim!

[center][img]http://static-2.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/61297-3-1420261168.jpg[/img][/center]
[color=#38761d][b][i][size=3]Requirements[/size][/i][/b] 
[/color]-[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36425/?]Real Girls UNP textures[/url]

[color=#38761d][size=3][b][i]Install-NMM[/i][/b][/size][/color]
-Proceed to regular download process

[color=#38761d][size=3][b][i]Install-Manual[/i][/b][/size][/color]
-I have made the folder structure ready to drag and drop into your Skyrim directory
(Drag and drop data folder into Skyrim directory)

[color=#38761d][size=3][b][i]F.A.Q[/i][/b][/size][/color]
-Will you make more tattoo sets?
Yes, I have recantly become more educated in the GIMP program, and will be honing my skills.

-Will you make them for RM overlays?
I don't know how to do that, but if someone tells me how, I will.
